 - This is the ZoneMinder Package Control script. This is used by the web interface and service scripts to control the execution of the system as a whole.
\par }{\b\insrsid150409 zmdc.pl}{\insrsid150409  - This is the ZoneMinder Daemo
n Control script. This is used by the web interface and the zmpkg.pl script to control and maintain the execution of the capture and analysis daemons, amongst others. You should not need to run this script yourself.
\par }{\b\insrsid150409 zmfilter.pl}{\insrsid150409 
 - This script controls the execution of saved filters and will be started and stopped by the web interface based on whether there are filters that have been defined to be autonomous. This script is also responsible for the automatic uploading of events t
o a 3rd party server.
